    <briefdescription>
<para>Monitors the platform for style changes. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This is a handle to the adaptor&apos;s style monitor which holds the platform&apos;s style information. It provides a signal when any aspect of the default style changes on the device. <simplesect kind="see"><para>Adaptor::GetStyleMonitor </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
